     FGCRWP21 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGCRPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGCRWP22 O   E                    DISK                      A
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60WKYM
     I                                        1   40WKY
     I                                        5   60WKM
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60WTIME
     I                                        7  140WDATE
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C                     TIME           SDATE
      *
     C                     READ GCRWP211                 80
     C           *IN80     DOWEQ'0'
     C                     EXSR #SB400
     C                     EXSR #SB500
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *-------------------------------------------*
      * GCRWP22                                   *
      *-------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB400    BEGSR
      *
